image_meta.caption: Crystal Tan contains minimal bronzer so that appears translucent when first applied. Crystal is the perfect spray tan solution for clients with a busy or discreet lifestyle. Upon application the solution is unnoticeable and gradually develops into a rich, golden tan during the development period (4-6hrs). Crystal Tan is enriched with natural and organic ingredients, such as Kakadu Plum Extract, Rosemary and Vitamin E.</br>Available in medium intensities, Crystal Tan is suitable for both fair to medium complexions.

image_meta.caption: BioTan is the perfect solution for those with sensitive skin or those looking for a natural glow. BioTan is packed full of the finest natural and organic ingredients including pineapple, mango, ginseng, blueberry, EcoCert DHA and Coffee Arabica. With sweet, caramel tones, BioTan is the nature-inspired, environmentally friendly tan that youu2019ve been looking for!
